**EDIT: i just posted few pictures from almost finished map (in csgo now)

i will never release this since its too realistic and i dont want to have ppl fight in my house lol.cya*** 

This is a very old map now,i was making in 2008-9.(I'm also inactive on fpsb since then :P)

it's in fact a remake of a real life home/neighborhood. I'm thinking to finish it,so i show it here for some opinions :D. It's mostly indoors at the moment,but outdoors part is gonna be worked soon. (I'm not sure what kind of map it is going to be yet probably not a de_map i just use that name for now.)

i know some parts have been worked with more detail when the basic layout isn't even finished yet,but that kept me motivated to work more on it when i was getting bored.

I will need some simple models(like stairs,furniture etc)for visual and optimization reasons.If someone has any modeling experience and is willing to help please contact me.(ofc you will get credits,and i will also give you something back for your work,just add me and we can discuss about it)
